data.description: Welcome to 101 Christopher Mills Road in Medford. If location is a top priority - this house should be on you must see list. Sitting on a large lot in a desired Medford Community this house offers beautiful updates and an amazing layout to accommodate all in comfort. As you step inside this house you will love the tranquil vibe with the neutral color pallet, pretty flooring throughout, sparkling light fixtures, and open sight lines connecting the spacious lower level to the upper level great room. The kitchen is a an entertainers dream offering you loads of storage and counter space. A full appliance package, stone counters and pretty tiled back splash. The breakfast bar creates options for casual dining for a crowd in comfort. The patio door allows you to enjoy the pretty view of the property and a retreat for warm weather enjoyment. Three nice sized bedrooms are down the hall . Two rooms share the updated main bath while the owners suite enjoys an en suite, pretty views of the yard and a walk in closet. The lower level offers an amazing rec room with a feature wall with a wood burning stove and pretty white washed brick. Another bedroom suite is located here-ideal for extended family. Step thru a door and find an ample laundry space-a home office and also a 2nd bank of cabinets for storage or a second work space. The entrance to your 2 car garage is conveniently located here as well. Outside you will be pleased with the amount of space for all your warm weather activates.  If you are looking for a move in ready-beautifully updated house - a short drive to downtown Medford and major roads, loads of shopping and dining options and a blue ribbon school district-your search is over.
